Instructor payment

  • Instructor payment

Fees for classes are collected by Olbgis from students via Stripe Payments or PayPal and are then remitted to the teacher via PayPal Payments or Wire transfer or by E-check.

  • Payouts
It takes 07 days for the Olbgis Company after withdrawal request to verify all information before to proceed each transaction. The third party service Fees (Paypal,Wise.....) are supported by the instructors. 

 

  • Instructor Earnings

After logged in as an Instructor, you will see at the bottom left corner of the Instructor dashboard you will see the section Earnings.

Deducted Commissions: are the commissions deducted by Olbgis company for services provided (55%).

Deducted Fees: are third party service Fees deducted when students are charging , neither Olbgis Company or the course instructor has nothing to do with it.
